



 _______________________________________________________________________________________
|											|
|				Arithmatic Types					|
|_______________________________________________________________________________________|
|											|
|	Types		Meaning					Minimum Size		|
|_______________________________________________________________________________________|
|											|
|	bool		boolean					NA			|
|	char		charachter	 			08 bits = 1 byte	|
|	wchar_t		wide character				16 bits = 2 bytes	|
|	short		short integer				16 bits = 2 bytes	|
|	int 		integer					16 bits = 2 bytes	|
|	long 		long integer				32 bits = 4 bytes	|
|	float		single-precision floating-point		06 Significant digit	|
|	double		double-precision floating-point		10 Significant digit	|
|	long double	extended-precision floating-point	10 Significant digit	|
|_______________________________________________________________________________________|
